     <h2>Description</h2>
     <p>soft boiled maize , with steamed African pear</p>
    <!-- Under the description, add an “Ingredients” heading followed by an unordered list of the ingredients needed for the recipe. -->
     <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>fresh maize</li>
        <li>african pear</li>
        <li>water</li>
    </ul>
    <!-- Finally, under the ingredients list, add a “Steps” heading followed by an ordered list of the steps needed for making the dish. -->
    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>dehusk fresh maize</li>
        <li>boil in water till soft</li>
        <li>wash African pear</li>
        <li>steam pear for about 15 mnutes</li>
        <li>allow both to cool and serve</li>
    </ol>
